{"tid":1931431,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"台灣新增23宗武漢肺炎確診 總數達到100宗","createTime":"2020-03-18T07:10:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-18T07:31:13.000Z","uid":265112,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"170f9921d1c830e837770cbc4adb70f923f32a95","tid":1931431,"uid":265112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T07:10:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/CiyvTnsSlfA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FCiyvTnsSlfA&d=V4yVQ1MiaEIlcmjbsyBqF8pe%2FvQB%2B59L3xQItPRvby0%3D&h=47646a33\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/CiyvTnsSlfA</a><br />\n<br />\n當中涉及本土兩例 外國輸入21例<br />\n<br />\n本土一例<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">無旅遊史</span></span>（#100），生活單純；另一個本土案例是埃及團團員的家庭親密接觸者。<br />\n<br />\n其中11例機場攔截後送，5例居家隔離發現，1例土耳其留學返台，1例機場檢疫車隊返家後步行就醫採檢隔離。<br />\n<br />\n土耳其旅遊團15人，目前共13人確診。"},{"pid":"ee94ca8d90af895c0da5bc230ed857168bb5da8c","tid":1931431,"uid":195894,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T07:11:55.000Z","msg":"隻病愈黎愈怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a2c8cec7844d84c9c09abe6fed7b94e8bdc3fd2","tid":1931431,"uid":56305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T07:12:33.000Z","msg":"肺炎抗共戰線 呢度有個行動真係好想大家都參與 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OAqP44x.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOAqP44x.jpg&h=88a996f7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kkJJ9wc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkkJJ9wc.jpg&h=cf92dbad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n想唔想外國疫症恐慌期間收到香港嘅鼓勵！<br />\n睇呢度：<br />\n我想做多次全球宣傳 正中國肺炎視聽<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1930664\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1930664</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c9b0efe034dba32af6480e46c27fd69f657666ae","tid":1931431,"uid":293557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T07:12:47.000Z","msg":"生